subtitleNullable: Images of LEGO and unknown bricks for classification purposes
descriptionNullable:
### Context

Dataset for the "Emerging technologies tech talk" held at VIA University Horsens in October 2019

### Content

Dataset contains images of LEGO and an unknown brand bricks, with image sizes containing just about the brick itself. The purpose of the dataset is to implement a classifier that can identify whether the given image corresponds to a LEGO brick or not.
